    public class DatastoreOperationLockManager
extends ReentrantOperationLockManager<DatastoreLockContext>
implements IDatastoreOperationLockManager, IDisposableService
    Controls cross-cutting exclusive write access to the terminology stores.

    This implementation unlocks all held locks on disposal.
